Nottstv The incident happened between 1am and 2.30am on Saturday May 5 where three men entered the service station and stole tobacco products. All three men were wearing dark clothing and two of them had face coverings. One of the men is described as white, aged between 22 and 28-years-old wearing a dark coloured knitted woolly hat, navy blue sweatshirt, dark Adidas tracksuit bottoms and dark green Adidas trainers. If you know any of the men, were in the area at the time or have any information, you are asked to call Notts Police on 101 quoting incident number 131 of May 5. Watch Here